title: Kindergarten Cut-Outs
description: Animals outlined with thick black line. Farm and domestic animals, including dogs, chickens, rabbits, bird and chipmunk or squirrel. Printed in colors on a green ground. The paper could be applied as is forming a frieze or the animals could be cut out and pasted to the wall or pinned to a fabric wallcoverings.
name: Frieze - cut outs
